<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About HULULU GARDEN</h2>
    <p class="about-intro">
      HULULU GARDEN is a small studio that turns real gourds into tiny
      characters with big personalities, and preserves flowers so they can
      bloom a little longer in your home.
    </p>

    <div class="about-features">
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Slow-Made Craft</h3>
        <p>Each gourd is dried, cleaned, carved, wood-burned and painted by hand. There's no mass production here – only patient, careful work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Every Piece Is Unique</h3>
        <p>Gourd shapes are all different, so every piece has its own pose and expression. Once a design is sold, it will never be exactly the same again.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <h3>Made for Everyday Joy</h3>
        <p>People tell us our gourds and flower frames make them smile on tough days. That's the whole point: small objects that quietly bring warmth and comfort.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-tags">
      <span>100% Handcrafted</span>
      <span>Each One of a Kind</span>
      <span>Gourd Art · Lamps · Pressed Flowers</span>
      <span>Custom Themes & Pet Portraits</span>
      <span>Perfect for Gifts & Home Decor</span>
    </div>

    <div class="about-cta">
      <a href="mailto:david.a.ocean@gmail.com?subject=Custom%20Gourd%20Order" class="btn">Custom Order · Email</a>
      <a href="#social" class="btn btn-outline">Follow Our Socials</a>
    </div>

    <p class="about-note">
      The custom order button opens your email app. Tell us what kind of
      gourd friend you'd like (theme, colors, size, budget), and we'll see
      what we can create.
    </p>

    <div class="about-cn">
      <h3>中文介绍 · About in Chinese</h3>
      <p>
        HULULU GARDEN 是一个以葫芦为主角的小手作品牌，也做花草标本和葫芦小夜灯。
        每一只葫芦都要经过晾晒、打磨、烙画、上色，一刀一笔慢慢完成；
        每一幅花框也都是把当季的花叶细细压制、重新排版，让它们在家里再"多开一阵"。
      </p>
      <p>
        我希望这些小东西可以陪你放在书桌、床头或是客厅一角，
        在你忙碌或者疲惫的时候，偷偷帮你存一点点快乐和浪漫。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--color-warm);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
